    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市、加密货币暴跌，债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/asian-stocks-crypto-currencies-plunge-as-bonds-rally-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市全线下跌，加密货币暴跌，债券上涨，因市场担心美联储对美国经济放缓的政策支持落后。加菲尔德·雷诺兹在“彭博社：中国秀”中对此进行了更多报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/asian-stocks-crypto-currencies-plunge-as-bonds-rally-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:18:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国服务业扩张呈现新势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/china-services-expansion-picks-up-in-fresh-sign-of-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项私人调查显示，中国服务业扩张速度为 5 月份以来最快，表明其韧性或可缓解官方数据疲软后人们对经济前景的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/china-services-expansion-picks-up-in-fresh-sign-of-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度企业准备迎接税收规则变化带来的回购热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/india-inc-braces-for-buyback-rush-ahead-of-changes-to-tax-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新的股票回购税规则于 10 月 1 日生效之前，印度企业正准备在未来几周增加股票回购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/india-inc-braces-for-buyback-rush-ahead-of-changes-to-tax-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
