    <item>
      <title>美国经济前景恶化，全球债券抹去今年的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济前景的担忧迅速恶化，刺激了对固定收益资产的需求，全球债券已经抹去了今年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金开盘大幅波动，因股价下跌震动投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周开始，金价经历了一段坎坷的走势，先是大幅下跌，随后又收复了大部分失地，因为交易员们评估了股市抛售和中东紧张局势的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险情绪加深，亚洲股市出现严峻里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国经济进一步放缓以及中东紧张局势加剧，投资者纷纷避开风险资产，亚洲股市在新的一周伊始大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本东证指数和日经指数从峰值下跌近 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日元升值、货币政策收紧以及美国经济前景恶化导致投资者信心崩溃，日本股市基准指数较上个月创下的历史高点下跌近 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japan-s-stock-rout-enters-third-day-with-nikkei-in-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>原油价格波动至七个月低点附近，因股市下跌抵消了伊朗风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东地区紧张局势加剧，金融市场普遍出现抛售，交易员担心伊朗可能对以色列采取报复性打击，油价在七个月低点附近波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银和东京电子的盈利有望因人工智能芯片需求而得到提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-tokyo-electron-get-ai-support-global-chip-wars-may-buoy-japan-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京电子有限公司 (Tokyo Electron Ltd.) 和 Lasertec Corp. 将紧随芯片巨头 SK 海力士公司 (SK Hynix Inc.) 和三星电子公司 (Samsung Electronics Co.) 之后公布业绩，这两家公司受益于人工智能使用的高带宽内存芯片的强劲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-tokyo-electron-get-ai-support-global-chip-wars-may-buoy-japan-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
